name: Ice Spice
description:
20 image 2,400 step 'Ice Spice' model trained in SD v1.5

Put <spicto> in your prompt to summon ice. A good place to start is "Portrait of spicto... xyz." This model might get updated with fewer steps for more consistent outputs.

We're going to start creating a lot more - https://www.gendesign.ai/
